---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Simplifying Business Exit Strategy | Summit Wealth Advisors" 
  description="We help business owners translate complexity into value with a clear exit strategy, focusing on tax mitigation and family wealth integration."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-primary text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-serif font-bold mb-4">Translate Complexity Into Value.</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        A successful business exit is more than a transaction. It's the culmination of your life's work. We provide the clarity to maximize its value.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-brand-neutral">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-lg">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-700 space-y-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-primary">Clarity Before, During, and After the Sale</h2>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            Selling your business is one of the most complex financial events you will ever navigate. Our primary goal is to simplify this process. We work alongside your legal and tax advisors to create a seamless strategy that integrates the proceeds of your sale into a cohesive, multi-generational financial plan.
          </p>
          <p class="leading-relaxed">
            We focus on critical areas of tax mitigation, investment management for the proceeds, and aligning this new liquidity with your familyâ€™s long-term goals.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-serif font-semibold text-primary">A Simple Checklist for Exit Readiness</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-4 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Define Your 'Summit':</strong> What does life look like after the sale? Clearly defining your personal financial goals is the most critical step.</li>
            <li><strong>Valuation Clarity:</strong> Have you had a recent, independent business valuation? Understanding your company's realistic market value is key.</li>
            <li><strong>Tax Strategy Review:</strong> Are your corporate structure and personal finances optimized for a potential sale? Early planning can save millions in taxes.</li>
            <li><strong>Post-Sale Investment Plan:</strong> Do you have a clear, disciplined plan for managing the proceeds to meet your lifestyle and legacy goals?</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Internal Linking -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-brand-neutral border-t border-slate-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-center text-primary mb-8">Explore Other Life Transitions</h3>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-8 text-center">
        <a href="/retirement" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary font-semibold">Find clarity in retirement planning &rarr;</a>
        <a href="/career-changes" class="text-primary hover:text-secondary font-semibold">Learn how we simplify complex compensation &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
